description:
Beautiful 1br apartment located in the heart of the West Village. Quiet street surrounded by the best restaurants, boutiques and NY greatest jazz bars. The Closest subway station is 3 minutes away where you can use the F,B,D,M,E,A,C,L,1 lines.

The apartment is on the 5th floor of a walk-up building. There's no elevator.
name: Amazing west village penthouse
